name: sccp
tagline: Project page for Sentence Comprehension as a Cognitive Process: A Computational Approach, by Shravan Vasishth and Felix Engelmann. Funded by the Volkswagen Foundation.
body:
### Welcome to our project page.

For the moment, please see our course materials from ESSLLI 2016,  [click here](http://www.ling.uni-potsdam.de/~vasishth/courses/ESSLLI2016VasishthEngelmann.html).

This web page will contain all code and other material related to this project. 

### Support or Contact
Please contact [Shravan](http://www.ling.uni-potsdam.de/~vasishth/) and [Felix](http://www.manchester.ac.uk/research/felix.engelmann) in case of questions.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
